headline: CME Group Sets New ADV Record of 35.9 Million Contracts In April, Up 36% Year Over Year
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today reported its April 2025 market statistics reached an all-time monthly average daily volume (ADV) record of 35.9 million contracts, an increase of 36% year-over-year.
